         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">South Yarra ¶  16/8/88 ¶  ¶ I feel obliged to you, esteemed Mr Best, for the honour that you have rendered me in dedicating such an elegant form of  ¶ Coleus ¶  to me, and I appreciate this the more s...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.08.16a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Heinrich Best</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M23, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS written by George Luehmann and signed by M. </p>
               </note>South Yarra 16/8/88</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich fühle mich Ihnen dankbar verpflichtet, geehrter Herr Best, für die Ehre welche Sie mir erwiesen haben, eine so elegante Form des <name key="Coleus">Coleus</name> mir zu zueignen, und ich erkenne dies um so mehr an, da ich so geringe Ansprüche an Ihre Güte habe. Vielleicht kann ich Ihnen in der einen oder anderen Weise nützlich sein, was mit Freude geschehen wird.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Durch meinen Unfall war ich verhindert an den Festlichkeiten des Turn Vereins in letzterer Zeit theil zu nehmen, doch hoffe ich bald wieder unter meinen Turner Freunden zu sein, obwohl ich jetzt noch bettlägerig bin</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">South Yarra<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Melbourne.</p>
               </note> 16/8/88</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I feel obliged to you, esteemed Mr Best, for the honour that you have rendered me in dedicating such an elegant form of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Coleus">Coleus</name>
               </seg> to me, and I appreciate this the more so because I have such slight claims on your kindness. Perhaps I can be useful to you in one way or the other, which will be done with pleasure.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I was prevented from taking part in the festivities of the Turn Verein recently by my accident,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. Melbourne's German Gymnastic Club. M had fallen off a tram on 31 July and was seriously injured (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>, 1 August 1888, p. 7).</p>
               </note> but I hope to be soon among my gymnast friends again, although I am still now bedridden.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Coleus">Coleus</name>
            </p>
         </div>
